{"tid":1524381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣組係咪應該或一輯英文漫畫，諷刺好多打著自由、民主嘅西方國家對香港視而不到","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T17:13:16.000Z","uid":143499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"05014a98e82fd3469710841dd5e66ffb6c7fe55b","tid":1524381,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:06:51.000Z","msg":"做之前可以行兩下會唔會帶來反效果，不過純粹提出新意見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三個月內，示威者都唔會做出一啲過份違反人性嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n但係警察同香港政府嘅道德底線一日比一日低，暴力的日比一日升級<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n西方世界政府嚟講除咗美國叫做少少嘢之外，其他根本who Fucking cares?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我諗係唔係應該整一啲英文嘅漫畫文宣諷刺佢哋，主要傳達比外國民眾，等佢哋向自己政府施壓"},{"pid":"aaa6c1523cab8e7433860371f1786d52363ee135","tid":1524381,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:07:43.000Z","msg":"幫手推到文宣組睇到"},{"pid":"3b2ba7fb58204bd84caeafb7d5dadb4c77340e61","tid":1524381,"uid":299171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:08:14.000Z","msg":"唔好責難人"},{"pid":"e79b5a553067c6e5016f856de03758a63b555d08","tid":1524381,"uid":187640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:09:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0ab2457b4728560daf044fd702167f9af687088","tid":1524381,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3b2ba7fb58204bd84caeafb7d5dadb4c77340e61","tid":1524381,"uid":299171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:08:14.000Z","msg":"唔好責難人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:09:39.000Z","msg":"仲責乜難<br />\n都就嚟緊急法<br />\n連登都無得上<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"2e3173a26c3a78e0b9be3a94deacaa2ea6a4e674","tid":1524381,"uid":299171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:10:56.000Z","msg":"呢個點睇<br />\n<br />\n三幅圖<br />\n<br />\n圖一<br />\n標題：Europe without America<br />\n圖畫：歐洲地圖插滿納粹旗<br />\n<br />\n圖二<br />\n標題：Asia without America<br />\n圖畫：東亞地圖插滿旭日旗<br />\n<br />\n圖三<br />\n標題：Hong Kong without America<br />\n圖畫：警暴相"},{"pid":"76f30d938d4355f00